Do not be so deluded that you can assume that you may play with anyone you choose or when you choose.  You are the plaything and always have been.  You now dance on a string like a profane little puppet.  Just wind you up and watch you dance.  You always play the same song and dance the same dance.  Just like a puppet there is never anything original.<br><br>
If you haven't figured out Cookie has been playing with you then you have made a grave mistake.  He told you long ago that he toyed with you and enjoyed winding you up.  Sounds to me as if you are the pack toy.  Watch it because I think you are going to be wound a lot tighter.  You threw out the rules.<br><br>
The informed would call you the pack Omega.  Look that one up.  I bet Ed knows the answer.  You should be able to figure it out.<br><br>
Are you beginning to wonder if you will no longer find dialogue here.  Or do you prefer to talk to yourself.<br><br>
Victim of history, think not.  To be a victim you have to allow yourself to be victimized.  A matter of choice.
